com.facebook.buck.core.rules.impl

Class SymlinkPack

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.rules.impl.SymlinkPack
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AddsToRuleKey, Symlinks

    public class SymlinkPack
extends Object
implements Symlinks
    Class compose multiple separate Symlinks and present them as a single Symlinks.

    This abstraction allows descriptions to: 1) avoid expensive symlink map merging into a monolithic SymlinkMap and 2) combine links from otherwise incompatible SymlinkMap and SymlinkDir groups.
